### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
SiMPLE Engine 4 is the 4th iteration of the Simple Java Games Engine developed by iPeer of SiMPLE Studios. Currently, the engine is still heavily in development but it free for anyone to use and modify so long as credit is given.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
name: SiMPLE Engine 4 - A Simple Java Games Engine
